An ji wani tashin hankali a tsakanin wasu 'yan majalisa game da shawarar da aka yi na canza taken su zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan shawara ta samo asali ne daga shirye-shiryen canza sunan majalisar a cikin majalisar dokokin Wales.
'Yan majalisa a duk faɗin siyasa suna damuwa cewa wannan zai zama abin ba'a.
