A wannan yanayin, ana furta harafin W a cikin Welsh kamar yadda ake furta harafin U a cikin Turanci na Yorkshire.
Kwamitin majalisar, wanda a halin yanzu yake cikin shirin kawo sauye-sauye a cikin sunaye, ya ce: "Yanke shawara na karshe game da duk wani abin da za a kira mambobin majalisar zai zama abin tattaunawa ga mambobin majalisar".
