Wataƙila fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ya ambata a ranar Juma'a sun kalli wannan shaidar.
Kamfanin ya yi amfani da ƙididdigar masu sauraro na CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
