Ko da yake ma'aikatan World Vision daga Donggala sun samu nasarar isa birnin Palu lafiya, inda ma'aikatan suka yi gudun hijira a karkashin shingen labule a cikin farfajiyar ofishin su, sun fuskanci al'amuran lalacewa a hanya, in ji Doseba.
"An gaya mini cewa sun ga gidaje da yawa da aka rushe", in ji shi.
