Makarantun Scottish masu zaman kansu suna riƙe da tsarin karatun ƙwarewar ilimi kuma wannan ya ci gaba a cikin 2018 tare da wani jerin fitattun sakamakon jarabawa, wanda aka ƙarfafa ta hanyar nasara ta mutum da na gama gari a cikin wasanni, zane-zane, kiɗa da sauran ƙoƙarin gama gari.
Tare da ɗalibai sama da 30,000 a duk faɗin Scotland, waɗannan makarantun, waɗanda The Scottish Council of Independent Schools (SCIS) ke wakilta, suna da burin samar da mafi kyawun sabis ga ɗaliban su da iyayensu.
