Sau biyu kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup wata kungiya ta dawo daga rabuwa da maki hudu ta shiga cikin wasan singles, kodayake a matsayin mai farawa, kungiyar Furyk tana buƙatar daidaitawa kawai don kare kofin.
