China ta ba da rahoton karuwar masu cutar HIV/AIDS da kashi 14 cikin dari
China ta sanar da karuwar mutane 14% da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar, in ji majiyoyin da ke kula da lafiyar jama'a.
Kusan 40,000 an ba da rahoton sababbin al'amuran a cikin kashi na biyu na 2018.
Yawancin sababbin cututtukan na kamuwa ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya nuna canji da aka samu a dā.
A wasu yankuna na ƙasar Sin, cutar HIV ta yaɗu a dā ta wurin ƙarin jini da aka yi wa mutane.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da kwayar cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, a cewar jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taron da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Ko da yake shekara shekara, adadin mutanen da suke da cutar HIV da kuma AIDS a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a tsakanin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
A shekarar 1997, an cire laifi daga luwadi a China, amma har yanzu ana nuna wariya ga 'yan luwadi.
Saboda al'adun gargajiya na ƙasar, wasu bincike sun kimanta cewa kashi 70-90 na maza da suke jima'i da maza suna yin aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtukan da ake samu a cikin jima'i suna faruwa ne saboda rashin yin amfani da rigakafi a lokacin jima'i.
A shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar kanjamau ga kowa a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance cutar.
