A yau, al'ada ce a nemi duk wani sabon fim da ke magana game da Brexit, kuma wannan ya shafi wannan sabon fim ɗin wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English, wanda aka fara a 2003 kuma aka sake dawo da shi a 2011 tare da Johnny English - The Rebirth.
