Akwai wani lokaci ko biyu masu ban sha'awa a wannan fitowar ta Johnny English ta karshe.
Na ji daɗin yadda Johnny English yake zuwa kusa da jirgin saman nan a cikin kayan yaƙi na ƙarni na farko, kuma masu kai na sun yi ta ƙwanƙwasa ƙwanƙwasawa a kan kwalkwali.
