Abin dariya ya zama kamar an yi shi ne ga yara maimakon manya kuma a wurina, Johnny English na rashin hankali ba shi da asali kuma ba a yi shi ba kamar wasan kwaikwayo na fim na Atkinson lokacin da yake wasa Mr Bean.
