Amurka na iya amfani da sojan ruwa wajen hana Rasha fitar da makamashin ta - Sakataren cikin gida
Washington na iya, idan ya cancanta, amfani da sojin ruwanta don hana samar da makamashin Rasha a kasuwa, har da na yankin Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda aka ruwaito daga Washington Examiner.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa shigar da Rasha a Siriya - musamman, inda take aiki a bisa gayyatar gwamnati mai shari'a - wani hujja ce don bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne suna son su yi ciniki a kan makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma bisa ga masu kula, akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyi da za a bi da wannan.
Amurka na da damar, ta hanyar sojan ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa na bude kuma idan ya zama dole, za a iya yin amfani da jirgin ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa makamashinsa ba zai shiga kasuwa, in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi magana da wadanda ake tuhuma a wani taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke kiran kanta 'muryar masu amfani da makamashi' a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta dabarun Washington da tattaunawar da ake yi da Rasha da Iran, yana mai cewa, a zahiri, abu daya ne.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziƙi a kan Iran da Rasha ya fi ko kaɗan, ya ce, don yin amfani da kuɗi da kuma maye gurbin mai", in ji shi, yana mai cewa Rasha "ba ta da amfani sosai", da kuma "tattalin arzikin da ya dogara da burbushin mai".
An yi wannan furucin ne saboda gwamnatin Trump ta shiga wani shiri na neman fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, wanda zai maye gurbin Rasha, wanda a ganinsa ya fi kowacce kasa a Turai.
Don cimma wannan buri, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, suna ƙoƙari su shawo kan Jamus ta fice daga Nord Stream 2, wani "shirin da bai dace ba" wanda, a cewar Trump, ya sa Berlin ta zama "kurkuku" ga Moscow.
Moscow ta sha nanata cewa wannan aikin na gas mai nauyin dala biliyan 11 da ake kira Nord Stream 2 wanda aka tsara shi ne don ninka karfin mai da ake da shi na yanzu zuwa mita biliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ta ce, Washington ta yi tsayayya da wannan shirin ne saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki, kuma hakan ya nuna rashin adalci.
"Ina ganin muna da ra'ayin cewa bai kamata a yi amfani da makamashi a matsayin hanyar matsa lamba ba, kuma ya kamata a bai wa masu amfani da makamashi damar zaban masu kawo su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak, bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
