A ranar Juma'a da safe masu zanga-zangar sun yi ta maimaita taken "November is coming!" a yayin zanga-zangarsu a zauren majalisar dattijai, lokacin da 'yan Republican da ke da iko a kan Kwamitin Shari'a suka zabi su ci gaba da takarar Kavanaugh duk da shaidar da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford ta bayar, kamar yadda Mic ya ruwaito.
"Jimillar 'yan Democrat da kuma kwarin gwiwarsu suna da yawa", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani manazarcin siyasa mai zaman kansa.
"Mutane sun ce sun riga sun yi tsayi; hakan gaskiya ne.
