A ranar Lahadi ne fadar White House ta ce, za a iya jinkirta ganawar da Donald Trump ke yi da mataimakin sakataren shari'a Rod Rosenstein har tsawon mako guda, yayin da ake ci gaba da takaddama kan alkali mai shari'a Brett Kavanaugh.
Rosenstein ya jagoranci aikin mai gabatar da kara na musamman Robert Mueller wanda ke binciken sa hannu da Rasha ta yi a zaben, da alakar da ke tsakanin masu ba Trump shawara da Rasha, da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban adalci.
Tunanin cewa Trump zai iya korar mataimakin sakataren shari'a, da kuma yin watsi da 'yancin Mueller, ya zama abin da ake ta jita-jita a Washington na tsawon watanni.
A farkon watan, New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein yana magana ne game da sanya bel don yin rikodin tattaunawa tare da Trump da kuma ƙoƙarin cire shugaban ta hanyar 25th Amendment.
Rosenstein ya musanta labarin.
