A maimakon haka, an sanar da wani taro da za a yi da shi a ranar Laraba tare da Trump, wanda a lokacin yana Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York.
Trump ya ce zai fi son kada ya kori Rosenstein, amma sai aka dage ganawar don kauce wa rikici da sauraron sauraron karar da kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai ya yi inda Kavanaugh da wata mata da ta zarge shi da fyade, Dakta Christine Blasey Ford, suka ba da shaida.
