Wani dan majalisar Scotland, Jeane Freeman, ya aika da wasikar kasa da watanni shida kafin Birtaniya ta fice daga EU.
Gwamnatin Scotland ta riga ta yi alkawarin biyan kudin neman zama a matsayin mazaunin gari ga 'yan asalin EU da ke aiki a cikin ayyukan gwamnati.
A cikin wasikar Minista Freeman ya rubuta cewa: 'A duk lokacin bazara akwai ci gaba da tattaunawa tsakanin Burtaniya da EU kan Brexit, wanda zai kai ga yanke shawara a kaka.
