Saboda haka, ina so in sake jaddada godiyata a yau ga gudummawar da dukan ma'aikatan suka bayar, ba tare da la'akari da ƙasarsu ba.
Ma'aikata daga ko'ina cikin EU da kuma wajenta suna kawo gogewa da ƙwarewa masu amfani waɗanda ke ƙarfafa da kuma inganta aikin sabis na kiwon lafiya, da amfani ga marasa lafiya da kuma al'ummomin da muke yi wa hidima.
