Aƙalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a sakamakon girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da tsunami da suka afka wa birnin Palu na ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar majiyoyin hukuma, kuma ana sa ran adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai ƙaru.
An dakatar da sadarwa kuma ba a sami wani bayani daga yankin Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da tsakiyar girgizar kasa mai girman 7.5.
Bayan bala'in, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 daga Palu.
Ga wasu bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birni na lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke a ƙarshen bakin bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi kuma yana da yawan mutane kusan 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka faru, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa.
Donggala yanki ne wanda ya shafi fiye da 300 km (180 mi) na gabar tekun a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Regency, wani yanki ne na lardin da ke da alhakin lardin, yana da kusan mazauna 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan hanyoyin samun tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya kuma musamman yankin Donggala na gabar teku.
Ma'adinai na nickel ma wani muhimmin aiki ne a lardin, amma ya fi mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a gabar tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun fuskanci tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Tsaro ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami ya rutsa da yammacin Donggala a 1996 inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin Pacific Ring of Fire, kuma sau da yawa girgizar ƙasa tana aukuwa a ƙasar.
Ga wasu cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka fi ƙarfin a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar tekun yammacin lardin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa kasashe 14 tare da kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: An samu girgizar kasa mai karfi a yammacin Sumatra a tsakanin karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin teku a Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa yankin kudu na Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, inda ta haifar da tsunami da ta afkawa gabar kudancin tsibirin inda ta kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta afka kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai, a gabar Sumatra, inda ta haifar da tsunami mai girman mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Wani karamin girgizar kasa ya afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, inda ya haifar da barna da fargaba a tsakanin mutanen da ke tuna da girgizar kasa da tsunami da aka yi a shekarar 2004.
A wannan yanayin, babu tsunami amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a ƙarƙashin kango.
2018: Wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, yawancinsu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta rushe dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido suka makale.
An kama ɗan fari na Sarah Palin a kan zargin cin zarafin mata
