Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun bukaci a yanke hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wadanda ake zargi da kai hare-haren ta'addanci a birnin New York.
Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun nemi a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ya kai harin da ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a taba yi wa wani laifi ba tun a shekarar 1953.
Saipov, 30, ana zarginsa da amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don ya bi ta hanyar titin keke a kan titin West Side Highway a cikin Lower Manhattan ta hanyar shiga cikin masu tafiya da masu hawa keke a watan Oktoba.
Bisa ga sharuddan da ke cikin dokar da ta shafi hukuncin kisa a Kudancin New York, don a yanke hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da ganganci kuma ya yi wa mutane rauni da gangan.
Bisa ga takardar kotu, waɗannan tuhume-tuhume biyu za su iya kai ga hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da tuhume-tuhume 22 da suka hada da tuhume-tuhume takwas na kisan kai da kuma hada kai, wanda ake amfani da shi a shari'o'in aikata laifuka, da kuma tuhume-tuhume guda daya na lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce wannan harin ya bukaci "tsara da kuma shiri sosai", sun kuma ce yadda Saipov ya aikata wannan harin "abin kiyayya ne, mugunta ne, kuma lalatacce ne".
Sanarwar ta ce "Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi barna, ya yi laifi, kuma ya yi asara ga iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco".
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne 'yan Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun wuce tun lokacin da kotun kudancin New York ta yanke hukunci na karshe a kan hukuncin kisa.
An zargi mutumin da ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da kisan wasu 'yan kasuwa biyu, amma a ƙarshe aka yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a kurkuku a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009.
A New York ne aka yi hukuncin kisa na karshe a 1953 a kan shari'ar da aka yi wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka zarge su da aikata leƙen asirin ƙasa, da kuma ba da bayanan sirri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Yaƙin Cacar Baki shekara biyu da suka wuce.
