Park Byeong-seug, ta ambaci bayanan da ma'aikatar sulhu ta Koriya ta Kudu ta bayar, ta ce an samu 'yan gudun hijira 1,127 a shekarar da ta gabata, idan aka kwatanta da 2,706 a shekarar 2011.
