Ta yaya yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya fa'idantar da Beijing
An yi ta bugun bugun wuta a yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, kuma yayin da yaƙin bai ƙare ba, masana sun ce rikici tsakanin Amurka da Sin na iya zama da fa'ida ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya riga ya yi gargadin farko a wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, da suka hada da bangarorin hasken rana, da karafa da kuma aluminum.
Babban tashin hankali ya faru a wannan makon tare da sabon haraji kan kayayyaki da suka kai dala biliyan 200 (euro biliyan 175) wanda ke nufin cewa za a sanya haraji kan rabin kayayyakin da ke fitowa daga China.
Beijing ta mayar da martani da irin wannan matakan ta hanyar sanya haraji na kashi biyar zuwa goma a kan kayayyakin Amurka biliyan 60.
China ta yi alkawarin mayar wa Amurka da martani, kuma ba zai yiwu ba kasar da ke da tattalin arziki na biyu a duniya ta sake yin hakan nan ba da jimawa ba.
Idan Washington ta janye, za a ba da ita ga bukatun ta, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a bainar jama'a zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Amma masana sun yi imanin cewa idan Beijing ta yi amfani da matakan da ta dauka, to, matsalolin da ke tattare da takaddamar kasuwanci da Amurka za su iya yin tasiri a kan Sin a cikin dogon lokaci, ta hanyar rage dogaro da juna.
"Gaskiyar cewa wani gagarumin mataki na siyasa daga Washington ko Beijing zai iya haifar da yanayin farko na rushewar tattalin arziki a cikin kasashen biyu ya fi hatsari fiye da yadda aka sani", in ji Abigail Grace, mai binciken Asiya a Cibiyar Nazarin Sabuwar Tsaro ta Amurka.
Syria ta shirya don dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar, in ji Ministan Harkokin Waje
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta marabci 'yan gudun hijirar da za su koma gidajensu, kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina kasar da ta yi shekaru bakwai ana yaki.
A gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce halin da ake ciki a kasar na samun ci gaba.
"Yanzu yanayin ya fi kwanciyar hankali da tsaro a yankin saboda ci gaba da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da aikin dawo da yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don dawo da yanayin da ya saba.
Yanzu haka akwai dukkan yanayi da za su ba da damar 'yan gudun hijira su koma ƙasar da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan da ƙasashen suka ɗauka na tattalin arziki da suka shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa sama da 'yan Siriya miliyan biyar da dubu hamsin ne suka tsere daga kasar tun bayan barkewar rikicin a 2011.
Sauran mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a Syria suna bukatar taimakon agaji.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Siriya za ta amince da taimakon da za a ba ta don sake gina kasar da aka yi wa katangar.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba zai karbi duk wani taimako da ya danganci sharuɗɗa ko daga waɗancan ƙasashe da suka tallafawa tawayen ba.
Turai ta yi nasara a gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Tawagar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta doke ta Amurka da ƙimar ƙarshe na 17.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a waje da Paris, Faransa.
A sakamakon haka, Amirka ta yi rashin nasara sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta ci gasar Ryder ba a Turai tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kofin ne a lokacin da tawagar kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin doke Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa kwallo a cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na par 3 ya ba da nasara ga Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan na Italiya ya yi fice a duk lokacin da ya buga, yana daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara buga gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya sha kashi da maki 5 & 4 daga dan wasan Danish mai karancin matsayi Thorbjorn Olesen na kungiyar Turai.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowa a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya yi nasara da dan wasan Ingila Ian Poulter wanda ya yi nasarar lashe kofin Ryder Cup na karshe.
Wani tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup, dan kasar Spain Sergio Garcia wanda ya buga wasanni takwas, ya zama dan wasan Turai da ya fi cin nasara a tarihin gasar da maki 25.5.
"Ba na yawan yin kuka, amma yau ba zan iya daina yin hakan ba.
Shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Na yi farin ciki sosai da na sake lashe kofin.
Wannan nasara ce ta tawagar kuma ina farin cikin bayar da gudummawata", in ji Garcia bayan nasarar da aka samu a gasar Turai.
Ya ba da shaida ga dan kasarsa John Ram wanda ya doke Tiger Woods da ci 2 da 1 a wasan da ya buga ranar Lahadi.
Rahm mai shekara 23 ya ce, "Idan na yi tunanin cewa na girma ne da kallon wasannin da yake yi, to ina alfahari da cewa na doke Tiger Woods".
Woods ya yi rashin nasara a duka wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa kuma yanzu haka, ya lashe gasar Ryder Cup sau 13, ya sha kaye sau 21, kuma ya yi nasara sau uku.
Wannan ƙididdiga ce mai ban mamaki idan ka yi la'akari da cewa shi ne ɗaya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na ko'ina, da ya lashe manyan kofofi 14, na biyu kawai ga Jack Nicklaus.
Team USA sun yi duk karshen mako suna neman hanyar da za su bi, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau sun yi wasan golf mai kyau a duk gasar.
Kyaftin din Amurka Jim Furyk ya ce bayan da tawagarsa ta kasa yin nasara, "Ina alfahari da wadannan 'yan wasan saboda sun yi gwagwarmaya.
A wani lokaci da safe, mun matsa wa ƙungiyar Turai.
Mun yi watsi da wannan dama.
Ka gaishe da Thomas.
Babban kyaftin ne shi.
Dukkan 'yan wasansa 12 sun nuna hali mai kyau.
Zan yi aiki da PGA ta Amirka da kuma kwamitin Ryder Cup kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan yara 12 kuma ina alfaharin zama shugabansu.
Mun yi amfani da dukan ƙarfinmu.
Amma sun fi mu wasa".
Sabuntawa game da ruwan sama: Ragewa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da Hukumar Kifi da Halittu ta Florida ta fitar kwanan nan ya nuna cewa an sami raguwar ruwan teku a wasu sassan yankin Tampa Bay.
FWC ya ce yanayin furewa, wanda ke nuna raguwar maida hankali, yana bayyane a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier.
Furen ruwan jan-ja ya kai kimanin kilomita 130 daga bakin teku daga arewacin Pinellas County zuwa kuducin Lee County.
Wuraren sun kai nisan mil 10 daga garin Hillsborough amma sun fi na makon da ya gabata yawa.
An kuma ga ruwan sama a yankin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata an bayar da rahoto kan matsakaicin taro a cikin Pinellas County ko kuma a gabar tekun, a ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a gabar tekun Hillsborough County, daga ƙananan taro zuwa manyan taro a Manatee County, daga ƙananan taro zuwa manyan taro a Sarasota County ko kuma a gabar tekun, daga ƙananan taro zuwa matsakaicin taro a County Charlotte, daga ƙananan taro zuwa manyan taro a Lee County ko a gabar tekun, da ƙananan taro a County Collier.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotannin cututtuka na cutar a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da kuma Collier.
A makon da ya gabata, ba a sami wata cutar a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba.
